<emphasis id="B937B072FFC8FFF4A0A7FDF1FED8FDE1" bold="true" box="[198,361,538,564]" pageId="2" pageNumber="23">Distribution:</emphasis>
— 
<taxonomicName id="4C4317E3FFC8FFF4A1E7FDF1FDC3FDE6" authorityName="Iganci &amp; Miotto" authorityYear="2011" box="[390,626,538,563]" class="Magnoliopsida" family="Fabaceae" genus="Adesmia" kingdom="Plantae" order="Fabales" pageId="2" pageNumber="23" phylum="Tracheophyta" rank="species" species="sessilifolia">
<emphasis id="B937B072FFC8FFF4A1E7FDF1FDC3FDE6" box="[390,626,538,563]" italics="true" pageId="2" pageNumber="23">Adesmia sessilifolia</emphasis>
</taxonomicName>
is only known from the central-western part of 
